<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="01b" n="11">누회 녀공과  밥 먹으며</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="01b" n="12">後護妻子</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="01b" n="12">누호의 안 녀공의 안와  밥 먹더니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="chi" page="01b-02a" n="13">頗厭呂公</sent>
